quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  99,1,When the earth is shaken to her (deepest) Convulsion
  99,2,And the earth throws up her burdens (from within)
  99,3,"And man cries (out in great pain): \"What is the matter with her"
  99,4,On that Day will she (the earth) declare her news
  99,5,"For that (Day), your (Mighty) Lord will have given her (the earth) His (Allah's) Order"
  99,6,"On that Day will men proceed in groups sorted out, to be shown the deeds that they (had done)"
  99,7,"Then anyone who has done an atoms weight of good, Shall see it"
  99,8,"And anyone who has done an atom’s weight of evil, Shall see it"